data.eml:eml: A new species of Leptolalax (Anura: Megophryidae) from Laos

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Phimmachak, Sompouthone, Sivongxay, Niane (2010): A new species of Leptolalax (Anura: Megophryidae) from Laos. Zootaxa 2681: 35-46, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.199342
